Subject: [PATCH] drm/msm/dpu1: don't choke on disabling the writeback connector
Mime-version: 1.0
Content-type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-transfer-encoding: 8bit
Git-commit: d9f55e2abfb933818c772eba659a9b7ab28a44d0
